# Project purpose

One-page website for **MobilKlime** — a mobile automotive air-conditioning service.
The technician travels to the customer's location (Beograd, Lazarevac, Obrenovac,
Aranđelovac, Lajkovac) and performs the inspection or service there.
Primary conversion: phone call. Secondary: WhatsApp/Viber message. No contact form.

# Source of truth

Before making changes, read: AGENTS.md, then docs/PROJECT_CONTEXT.md, CLIENT_DATA.md,
CONTENT.md, DESIGN_SYSTEM.md, ANIMATION_SYSTEM.md, SEO_PERFORMANCE.md, ROADMAP.md,
DECISIONS.md, HANDOFF.md. Repository documentation has priority over assumptions
and chat memory.

# Workflow

- Work only on the current roadmap phase (docs/ROADMAP.md). Do not implement future phases.
- Do not rebuild the whole website when asked for a focused change.
- Do not change approved decisions (docs/DECISIONS.md) without documenting the reason.
- Update DECISIONS.md and HANDOFF.md after every phase, then git commit.
- Never invent business facts: phone numbers, prices, reviews, statistics, locations,
  working hours, gas types, experience, certifications. Unknown data = `{{PLACEHOLDER}}`
  as defined in docs/CLIENT_DATA.md.

# Language

All website copy is Serbian, Latin script (`lang="sr-Latn"`). Documentation is Serbian.
Code identifiers, comments and commit messages are English.
